{"tid":1535484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我連發夢都見到黑警打人 I even dreamt about HKPF abuse HK citizens","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:27:51.000Z","uid":229502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b350a48a4143aec2baafd5385e7451f9609594a1","tid":1535484,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"雖然我只係一個和理非，雖然我連彈都未食過<br />\n<br />\n但係我依家連發夢都會見到黑警打人，仲要打撚埋自己<br />\n<br />\n雖然我冇真正畀黑警打過，我唔可以描述係點<br />\n<br />\n但係我已經畀呢個垃圾政府就嚟逼癲<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母發夢都見撚到黑警打人係乜撚嘢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有我想多謝全部勇武手足<br />\n<br />\n我哋用和理非嘅方法做唔到乜嘢，正正係你哋有勇氣去衝先可以令呢場革命持續<br />\n<br />\n多謝你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAlthough I am just a peaceful protester,<br />\nalthough I had never been attacked,<br />\nbut I dreamt that HKPF is abusing and hurting HK citizens, they even hurt me.<br />\n<br />\nBut I had never been &quot;truly&quot; hurt by the police, so I can't say what's that feeling.<br />\n<br />\nBut my point is I am nearly crazy because of this fxxking government.<br />\n<br />\nI mean WHY THE FXXK DO I DREAM ABOUT POLICE HURTING PEOPLE?<br />\n<br />\nAnd I want to thank all of the brothers and sisters.<br />\n<br />\nWe peaceful protesters can't do much, you help this revolution keeps going.<br />\n<br />\nTHANK YOU VERY MUCH <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c82bb496442d1c60373390fca14a5ab9e66c2ee","tid":1535484,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a81826b2e7ee914b02e6dfee75a0fcba7b975c22","tid":1535484,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"ご署名をお願いします！<br />\n香港における政府当局による強権的な動きをけん制するため、日本版『香港人権・民主主義法案』の議論を開始することを日本の国会議員に求めます。<br />\nPlease submit your signature!<br />\nWe are asking Japanese parliamentarians to start discussions on the Japanese version of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/rqWFBmbSp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FrqWFBmbSp4&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDdHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=4e54ff2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/rqWFBmbSp4</a> <br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手簽同share. Thank you."},{"pid":"7594f55e82bf5118ecbba4ea1058e44a82266721","tid":1535484,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\"